title: Women's Tennis Falls at No. 34 Texas Tech - UTRGV Athletics
content: Women's Tennis Falls at No. 34 Texas Tech  UTRGV Athletics
description: LUBBOCK – The University of Texas Rio Grande Valley (UTRGV) Vaqueros women's tennis team was defeated 4-0 by the No. 34 Texas Tech Red Raiders on Sunday at the McLeod Tennis Center.
